# Data Download Instructions

This project uses 6 open-access datasets.
Raw data files are not included in this repository 
due to file size. Download them from the sources below.

## 1. IBTrACS Cyclone Data
- URL: https://www.ncei.noaa.gov/products/international-best-track-archive
- File needed: ibtracs.NI.list.v04r00.csv
- Place in: data/raw/

## 2. ERA5 Rainfall
- URL: https://cds.climate.copernicus.eu
- Variable: total_precipitation
- Date range: May 2009, May 2020
- Region: 21-23°N, 88-89°E
- Place in: data/raw/era5_rainfall.nc

## 3. Census of India 2011
- URL: https://censusindia.gov.in
- Tables needed: Primary Census Abstract, block level
- District: South 24 Parganas
- Place in: data/raw/census_sundarbans_2011.csv

## 4. Sentinel-1 SAR Flood Maps
- URL: https://earthengine.google.com
- Dates: May 2009, May 2020
- Place in: data/raw/

## 5. IDMC Displacement Data
- URL: https://www.internal-displacement.org
- Place in: data/raw/displacement_sundarbans.csv
